# Copied here as documentation only. Do NOT put a real private key in this
# repo at all during the paper-trading phase -- it is not needed.
#
# When you later move to live trading (a separate, explicit phase), create
# a dedicated burn wallet yourself, fund it manually, and only then set:
#
# PK=your_dedicated_burn_wallet_private_key
# WALLET=0xYourBurnWalletAddress
# SIG_TYPE=0

# Optional: a Polygon RPC endpoint for reading the Chainlink BTC/USD feed
# (used by Bot 2). A free public RPC works fine for read-only calls.
POLYGON_RPC_URL=https://polygon-bor-rpc.publicnode.com
